message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $11,500. I believe it's a fair price considering its value. What do you think?
I appreciate your initial offer, but I was thinking more along the lines of $10,500. Would you be willing to meet me at this price?
Bob, I understand your perspective, but $10,500 is a bit too low for me. Could we settle at $11,000? It's a compromise I'm willing to make.
I appreciate your willingness to compromise, but I was thinking more along the lines of $10,750. Would you be willing to meet me at this price?
